---
title: Cheesy Bulgogi-Inspired Roll-Ups with Creamy Sesame Slaw
description: The table is set with this delicious mash-up between Korean bulgogi beef and Philly cheese steak! A sweet and savoury filling with ground beef and pork mix as well as bell pepper is wrapped and baked with Monterey cheese until ooey and gooey. Served with a refreshing coleslaw for flavour and texture balance!
